trans-unit.source: Allows Visual Studio to communicate internally with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio에서 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> 컨트롤과 내부적으로 통신할 수 있도록 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control is browsing a COM object and the user renames the object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> 컨트롤이 COM 개체를 찾는 동안 사용자가 개체의 이름을 바꾸면 발생합니다.

trans-unit.source: Only a change of value of the property that corresponds to DISPID_Name for the COM object raises the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComponentModel.Com2Interop.IComPropertyBrowser.ComComponentNameChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: COM 개체에 대 한 DISPID_Name에 해당 하는 속성의 값의 변경에만 발생는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComponentModel.Com2Interop.IComPropertyBrowser.ComComponentNameChanged> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: Closes any open drop-down controls on the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> 컨트롤에서 열려 있는 드롭다운 컨트롤을 모두 닫습니다.

trans-unit.source: Commits all pending changes to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> 컨트롤에 대해 보류 중인 모든 변경 사항을 커밋합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> successfully commits changes; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" />의 변경 사항이 성공적으로 커밋되면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Activates the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control when the user chooses **Properties** for a control in Design view.
trans-unit.target: 사용자가 디자인 뷰에서 컨트롤의 **속성**을 선택하면 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> 컨트롤을 활성화합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control is currently setting one of the properties of its selected object.
trans-unit.target: 현재 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> 컨트롤이 선택된 개체의 속성 중 하나를 설정하고 있는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control is currently setting one of the properties of its selected object; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> 컨트롤이 선택된 개체의 속성 중 하나를 설정하고 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The registry key that contains the user states.
Loads user states from the registry into the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control.

You can save some of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid> control states, such as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.PropertySort%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.HelpVisible%2A> properties, to the registry and load them the next time the user runs your application.
trans-unit.target: 일부를 저장할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid> 와 같은 컨트롤 상태는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.PropertySort%2A> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.HelpVisible%2A> 속성은 레지스트리 및을 다음에 사용자 응용 프로그램을 실행 하는 부하에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The registry key that contains the user states.
Saves user states from the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid" /> control to the registry.

You can save some of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid> control states, such as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.PropertySort%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.HelpVisible%2A> properties, to the registry and load them the next time the user runs your application.
trans-unit.target: 일부를 저장할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid> 와 같은 컨트롤 상태는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.PropertySort%2A> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PropertyGrid.HelpVisible%2A> 속성은 레지스트리 및을 다음에 사용자 응용 프로그램을 실행 하는 부하에 있습니다.
